@startuml
actor User
participant UI as "ImageEditor"
participant Proc as "ImageProcessor"
User -> UI: Изменить слайдер (яркость)
activate UI
UI -> Proc: reset()
activate Proc
Proc --> UI: current_image
deactivate Proc
UI -> Proc: adjust_brightness(factor)
activate Proc
Proc --> UI: updated_image
deactivate Proc
UI -> UI: display_current_image()
UI --> User: Предпросмотр
deactivate UI
@enduml